snippet.title: Knossu Gameplay
snippet.description:
Knossu, by Jonathan Whiting
http://jonathanwhiting.com/games/knossu/

I just noticed it on pcgamer.com, looked pretty cool.
Just like Antichamber, this game has a non-euclidean world.

10/10
